<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khua zakip ah tuanbia chim awk kan ngei, Lam dingmi hmuhsak tu
 tuanbia, Biatak le zaang-fahnak tuanbia, Daihnak le ceunak tuanbia,
 Daihnak le ceunak tuanbia.

[C1]
   Muihnak a lo lai, Khua a dei lai Chun ni lin caan a rung chuak lai,
   Dawtnak ceunak Jesuh pennak cu vawlei ah a rungtum lai.

[V2]
 Miphun kip sinah hlasak awk kan ngei, Bawipa leiah lung thleng tu hla,
 Hi hla nih chiatnak a tei lai, Fei le nam a khiah dih lai, Fei le nam a
 khiah dih lai.

[C2]
   Muihnak a lo lai, Khua a dei lai Chun ni lin caan a rung chuak lai,
   Dawtnak ceunak Jesuh pennak cu vawlei ah a rungtum lai.

[V3]
 Khuakip ah Thawngthabia thanh awk kan ngei, Van in mi uktu Pathian
 nih, A Fa Khamhtu a run thlah i, Pathan dawtnak a langhter, Pathian
 dawtnak a langhter.

[C3]
   Muihnak a lo lai, Khua a dei lai Chun ni lin caan a rung chuak lai,
   Dawtnak ceunak Jesuh pennak cu vawlei ah a rungtum lai.

[V4]
 Khuakip ah Khamhbawi hmuhsak awk kan ngei, Ngaih-chiatnak lam a zulmi
 kha; Amah thawngin miphun kip nih, Pathian dinnak an hngalh lai, Pathian
 dinnak an hngalh lai.

[C4]
   Muihnak a lo lai, Khua a dei lai Chun ni lin caan a rung chuak lai,
   Dawtnak ceunak Jesuh pennak cu vawlei ah a rungtum lai.</lyrics>
<title>KHUAKIP AH TUANBIA CHIM AWK KAN NGEI CH412</title>
<hymn_number>412</hymn_number>
</song>